---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="AeroFabric Solutions - Comprehensive Air Distribution Products">
  <Header />
  
  <Hero 
    title="Advanced Textile Air Solutions" 
    description="Cutting-edge engineering for precise, efficient air circulation across industries"
  />

  <main class="container products-page">
    <section class="product-categories">
      <div class="product-category air-socks">
        <h2 class="category-title glitch" data-text="Air Socks">Air Socks</h2>
        <div class="category-content">
          <div class="category-description">
            <p>Revolutionary textile-based air distribution systems designed for optimal air flow and environmental control. Our Air Socks represent the pinnacle of intelligent air management, combining advanced materials with precision engineering.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="product-specs">
            <div class="spec-grid">
              <div class="spec-item">
                <h3>Material Innovation</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Proprietary micro-perforated textile</li>
                  <li>Antimicrobial fabric treatment</li>
                  <li>UV and flame-resistant composition</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-item">
                <h3>Performance Metrics</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Air Distribution Efficiency: 95%</li>
                  <li>Temperature Uniformity: ±1.5°C</li>
                  <li>Pressure Drop: Minimal (0.2 Pa/m)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-item">
                <h3>Customization Options</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Custom lengths (1-50 meters)</li>
                  <li>Multiple perforation patterns</li>
                  <li>Color and branding options</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product-category air-distribution">
        <h2 class="category-title glitch" data-text="Air Distribution Systems">Air Distribution Systems</h2>
        <div class="category-content">
          <div class="category-description">
            <p>Intelligent air distribution solutions that transform how environments manage airflow. Our systems provide unparalleled control, ensuring optimal comfort, energy efficiency, and air quality across diverse applications.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="product-specs">
            <div class="spec-grid">
              <div class="spec-item">
                <h3>System Architecture</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Modular design</li>
                  <li>Smart sensor integration</li>
                  <li>IoT-enabled monitoring</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-item">
                <h3>Energy Efficiency</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Up to 40% energy savings</li>
                  <li>Dynamic airflow adjustment</li>
                  <li>Real-time performance optimization</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-item">
                <h3>Application Versatility</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Industrial facilities</li>
                  <li>Healthcare environments</li>
                  <li>Commercial spaces</li>
                  <li>Data centers</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product-category innovations">
        <h2 class="category-title glitch" data-text="Innovations & Specialties">Innovations & Specialties</h2>
        <div class="category-content">
          <div class="category-description">
            <p>At the forefront of textile air distribution technology, our R&D team continuously pushes boundaries. We develop groundbreaking solutions that redefine air management, focusing on sustainability, precision, and intelligent design.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="product-specs">
            <div class="spec-grid">
              <div class="spec-item">
                <h3>Technological Breakthroughs</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Nano-engineered textile membranes</li>
                  <li>Self-cleaning air distribution fabric</li>
                  <li>Adaptive thermal regulation</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-item">
                <h3>Sustainability Focus</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>100% recyclable materials</li>
                  <li>Carbon-neutral manufacturing</li>
                  <li>Reduced environmental footprint</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-item">
                <h3>Future Research Areas</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Quantum air flow modeling</li>
                  <li>Bio-mimetic textile design</li>
                  <li>AI-driven air distribution</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .products-page {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg, 
      var(--background-dark) 0%, 
      color-mix(in srgb, var(--background-dark) 90%, var(--secondary-color)) 100%
    );
  }

  .product-categories {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 60px;
  }

  .product-category {
    background: rgba(15, 25, 45, 0.7);
    border-radius: 15px;
    padding: 40px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .product-category:hover {
    border-color: var(--secondary-color);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.2);
  }

  .category-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
  }

  .category-description {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .spec-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .spec-item {
    background: rgba(10, 25, 47, 0.8);
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .spec-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
  }

  .spec-item h3 {
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .spec-item ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .spec-item ul li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.1);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .spec-item ul li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
</style>
